# Shopify Chat Assistant - Feature Roadmap

## 1. Core Authentication & Installation
- [ ] Shopify OAuth flow implementation
- [ ] Session management for merchants
- [ ] Proper scope handling for data access
- [ ] Merchant settings & configuration storage
- [ ] Multi-store support architecture

## 2. Enhanced Order Management
- [ ] Bulk order lookup functionality
- [ ] Advanced order filtering (by date, status, value)
- [ ] Order update notifications system
- [ ] Refund and cancellation handling
- [ ] Order history timeline view
- [ ] Payment status tracking
- [ ] Automated order status updates

## 3. Customer Service Suite
- [ ] Ticket management system
  - Create, assign, and track support tickets
  - Priority levels and SLA tracking
  - Automated ticket routing
- [ ] Customer conversation history
  - Timeline view of all interactions
  - Context preservation between chats
  - Note-taking system for agents
- [ ] Team collaboration features
  - Agent-to-agent chat
  - Ticket transfer system
  - Shared macros and snippets
- [ ] Multi-agent support
  - Agent availability status
  - Work distribution system
  - Performance tracking

## 4. Analytics & Reporting
- [ ] Customer Service Metrics
  - Response time tracking
  - Resolution rate monitoring
  - Customer satisfaction scores
  - Agent performance metrics
- [ ] Issue Analytics
  - Common problem identification
  - Peak time analysis
  - Topic clustering
- [ ] Custom Report Builder
  - Exportable reports
  - Scheduled report delivery
  - Custom metric creation

## 5. AI Enhancements
- [ ] Advanced Training System
  - Product catalog integration
  - Custom response templates
  - Merchant-specific training
- [ ] Intelligent Features
  - Sentiment analysis
  - Intent recognition
  - Automated categorization
  - Smart routing
- [ ] Product Recommendations
  - Context-aware suggestions
  - Cross-sell/upsell automation
  - Bundle recommendations

## 6. Merchant Configuration
- [ ] Visual Customization
  - Chat widget appearance
  - Custom branding options
  - Mobile responsiveness
- [ ] Operational Settings
  - Business hours management
  - Holiday scheduling
  - Language preferences
- [ ] Workflow Automation
  - Custom response rules
  - Triggered actions
  - Automated follow-ups

## 7. Integration Hub
- [ ] Shopify Integrations
  - POS system connection
  - Inventory sync
  - Customer profiles
- [ ] Third-party Connections
  - Shipping carriers
  - Help desk platforms
  - Email marketing tools
- [ ] API Access
  - Webhook management
  - Custom endpoint creation
  - API key management

## 8. Security & Compliance
- [ ] Data Protection
  - GDPR compliance tools
  - Data retention policies
  - Privacy controls
- [ ] Access Control
  - Role-based permissions
  - IP restrictions
  - Audit logging
- [ ] Merchant Isolation
  - Data segregation
  - Resource limits
  - Backup systems

## 9. Performance & Scaling
- [ ] Infrastructure
  - Load balancing
  - Rate limiting
  - Caching system
- [ ] Optimization
  - Response time improvements
  - Resource usage monitoring
  - Database optimization

## 10. Monetization
- [ ] Pricing Plans
  - Feature-based tiers
  - Usage-based billing
  - Custom enterprise plans
- [ ] Billing Management
  - Usage tracking
  - Automated billing
  - Payment processing
- [ ] Feature Controls
  - Feature flags
  - Plan restrictions
  - Upgrade prompts

